Name.ElementValue: SPLIT-HAND/FOOT MALFORMATION 1 WITH OR WITHOUT DEAFNESS

ClinVarAccession.SubmitterName: Department of Medical Genetics, Sanjay Gandhi Post Graduate Institute of Medical Sciences

Classification.Comment: CMA analysis revealed a deletion of 7.2Mb at chromosome 7q21.2. This region includes genes DYNC1I1, DLX5, DLX6, SLC25A13, SMAD9, PEG10, PPP1R9A, CDK6. This is a known region of split-hand/foot malformation-1 (SHFM1). Deletions of varying sizes are reported as pathogenic in ISCA and DECIPHER.
